{"tid":2370083,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"David Perry 獲港律政司委聘任主控　藍韜文：令人覺得有點唯利是圖","createTime":"2021-01-17T17:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T04:46:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"71467f17c187b63aa526836331cca38b1c885590","tid":2370083,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"高等法院上周就律政司在檢控前年 8 月 18 日維園非法集結案中，聘用英國御用大律師 David Perry 頒下判詞，批准律政司申請。英國外相藍韜文指北京會視聘請英國御用大律師檢控民主派人士，是公關突破，而大律師亦並非不可抗拒這些官司。他直言 David Perry 接辦此案，令人覺得唯利是圖（mercenary）。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文參選成下議院議員前，在外交部擔任人權問題律師，亦曾在海牙協助國際法庭處理戰犯法律工作。他表示自己不明白任何人如何「有良心」地處理這一案件。他今天在英國當地時間早上接受 BBC 政治編輯 Andrew Marr 視像訪問，認為大律師可以「行為守則」抗拒此案，他補充：「從北京的角度，這將是一場嚴重的公關突擊。坦白說，我認為人們看到這情況，會覺得有點唯利是圖（mercenary），當你去接這樣的案件」<br />\n<br />\n他在天空新聞節目直言，「我不明白任何人如何有良心，從我們已知領先世界的法律專業中，接過一宗案件，而案件將不得不按照北京當局的要求適用的國家安全法，這直接侵害、貶損了香港人的自由；而我理解，這就是David Perry 先生和泛民行動者在這宗案件中的關係。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/8-18-%E7%B6%AD%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E6%A1%88-david-perry-%E7%8D%B2%E6%B8%AF%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E5%A7%94%E8%81%98%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7-%E8%97%8D%E9%9F%9C%E6%96%87-%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%BA%E5%BE%97%E6%9C%89%E9%BB%9E%E5%94%AF%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-18-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25A1%2588-david-perry-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E8%2581%2598%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E8%2597%258D%25E9%259F%259C%25E6%2596%2587-%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2594%25AF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%259C%2596%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=eadc4438\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-18-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25A1%2588-david-perry-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E8%2581%2598%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E8%2597%258D%25E9%259F%259C%25E6%2596%2587-%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2594%25AF%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%259C%2596%2F&h=53345750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/8-18-%E7%B6%AD%E5%9C%92%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E6%A1%88-david-perry-%E7%8D%B2%E6%B8%AF%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E5%A7%94%E8%81%98%E4%BB%BB%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7-%E8%97%8D%E9%9F%9C%E6%96%87-%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%BA%E5%BE%97%E6%9C%89%E9%BB%9E%E5%94%AF%E5%88%A9%E6%98%AF%E5%9C%96/</a>"},{"pid":"8419958f09a33ddd9b6e4c806d4922193c0c13c6","tid":2370083,"uid":106,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:18:11.000Z","msg":"明明最初奶得最勁哥個係佢 死都唔比BNO平權又係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f67da25b33fb7592f679be0c7e3655023bd266a","tid":2370083,"uid":99243,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:18:55.000Z","msg":"制裁啦, 唔好得把口"},{"pid":"c71f4ead22b1623668579317e0ba01dedb218d40","tid":2370083,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d5033f09a2ed9d98de56eba8bb7b3fd828d96f","tid":2370083,"uid":304769,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8419958f09a33ddd9b6e4c806d4922193c0c13c6","tid":2370083,"uid":106,"like":3,"disli